      • getMinTime

        int getMinTime(java.lang.String objName,
             java.lang.String agent)
        Minimal time, according to the disRPG, in which a given agent can get this variable to have a given value (objName). Returns -1 if the given agent cannot assign the given value to this variable.
        Parameters:
        objName - Value name
        agent - Agent to generate the value
        Returns:
        Minimum time needed to reach that value by that agent; -1 if it is not reachable
